data.description: Welcome to this stunning 4-bedroom, 4-bath home nestled in the heart of Stetson Hills, boasting over 2100 sq ft of  living space. Minutes to Powers and Peterson SFB with a little longer drive to Fort Carson, this home is near to lots of amenities! With no HOA, this property offers the perfect blend of convenience and freedom. Step into a home with soaring vaulted ceilings in the primary living space with lots of natural light. Enjoy the ample room sizes, designed for comfort and functionality. This two-story home comes with a fully finished basement which includes the fourth bedroom and full bathroom, offering flexibility and additional living space. The primary suite treats you to a private balcony, leading to a spacious deck, and a vast backyard, providing an ideal setting for gatherings and outdoor entertainment. Discover the perfect blend of style, comfort, and convenience in this Stetson Hills gem.
